gui

Class RideListingPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • gui.DefaultView
      • gui.RideListingPanel

  • final class RideListingPanel
extends DefaultView
    This class creates the ride listing Pane and the components that make up the Pane. The calling class is responsible for adding the Pane of this class to its view to change the scene so that this view can be interacted with.
    Author:
    Brandon Bonebrake
